15namespace webrtc {
16
17const char* ResourceUsageStateToString(ResourceUsageState usage_state) {
18 switch (usage_state) {
19 case ResourceUsageState::kOveruse:
20 return "kOveruse";
21 case ResourceUsageState::kUnderuse:
22 return "kUnderuse";
23 }
24 RTC_CHECK_NOTREACHED();
25}
